com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities

Class BulkAdGroupRadiusTargetBid

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.internal.bulk.entities.SingleRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v10.bulk.entities.BulkAdGroupRadiusTargetBid

  • public class BulkAdGroupRadiusTargetBid
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity
    Represents one radius target bid within an radius target that is associated with an ad group. This class exposes the BulkRadiusTargetBid.setRadiusTargetBid(com.microsoft.bingads.v10.campaignmanagement.RadiusTargetBid) and BulkRadiusTargetBid.getRadiusTargetBid() methods that can be used to read and write fields of the Ad Group Radius Target record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Ad Group Radius Target at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=620257.

    One BulkAdGroupRadiusTarget exposes a read only list of BulkAdGroupRadiusTargetBid. Each BulkAdGroupRadiusTargetBid instance corresponds to one Ad Group Radius Target record in the bulk file. If you upload a BulkAdGroupRadiusTarget, then you are effectively replacing any existing bids for the corresponding radius target.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter

        public Status getStatus()
        Gets the status of the target.

        The value is Active if the target is available in the customer's shared library. The value is Deleted if the target is deleted from the customer's shared library, or should be deleted in a subsequent upload operation. Corresponds to the 'Status' field in the bulk file.
